      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented modelling procedure and independent peer review of model setup reduce risk of operator-induced errors.",
      "rationale": "Model setup procedure VP-FEA-007-P2 followed. Independent peer review of boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions performed by a second analyst. No discrepancies identified. Use error risk assessed as low."
