      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric dimensions sourced from traceable measurements with uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Ti-6Al-4V elastic modulus and yield strength from ASTM E8 coupon tests (n=5 per lot). Geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of production screws (n=5). Uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo sampling (1000 runs); 95th-percentile QoI spread reported. Input uncertainty adequately characterised."
    },
    {
