      "rationale": "All specimens tested at a single load rate (2 mm/min) and single fixture offset (5 mm). ASTM F1717 specifies this configuration, but the COU envelope includes off-nominal load rates relevant to dynamic loading scenarios. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this is a documented gap acknowledged in the credibility assessment."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
