      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA model inputs (geometry, material properties, boundary conditions) demonstrably match the as-tested specimen configuration.",
      "rationale": "FEA geometry updated to match CMM-measured specimen dimensions. Material properties assigned from lot-specific coupon test data. Fixture boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry as measured. Equivalency confirmed by pre-test FEA predictions within 5% of mean test results for pilot specimens."
    },
