      "rationale": "E/uval computed for stiffness (1.41), yield force (1.67), and force at 40 mm (1.55). All three below the 1.96 threshold. Mean absolute percentage errors 6.3%, 8.1%, and 7.4% respectively, all below the 10% acceptance bound. Output comparison criterion met for all QoIs."
